"help.title" = "Help & Feedback";
"help.manual.welcome_title" = "👋 Welcome to FunnyPixels";
"help.manual.welcome_desc" = "FunnyPixels is a global co-creation pixel map where your real-world movement creates pixel art. Walk with GPS to draw, join alliances to conquer territory, and explore a world painted by players everywhere.";
"help.manual.getting_started_title" = "Getting Started";
"help.manual.getting_started_desc" = "After launching FunnyPixels, you'll be asked to grant location permission — this is essential for GPS drawing.\n\nNavigation:\n- Map: Browse the global pixel canvas, see nearby players and territory\n- Feed: Social feed, drawing records, and data dashboard\n- Alliance: Join or create teams, level up together\n- Rank: Leaderboards with rank tiers and friend rankings\n- Me: Profile, daily tasks, achievements, and settings\n\nThe round button at the bottom right starts GPS drawing. Long press it to switch your drawing flag.\n\nQuick Stats: A floating widget on the map shows today's pixels, sessions, and daily task progress at a glance.";
"help.manual.gps_drawing_title" = "GPS Drawing";
"help.manual.gps_drawing_desc" = "GPS Drawing turns your real-world movement into pixel art on the map.\n\nHow to start:\n1. Move to the area you want to draw\n2. Tap the round button to start a GPS session\n3. Walk around — your path becomes pixels\n4. Tap Stop when finished\n\nTips:\n- Choose your flag before starting (personal color, avatar, or alliance flag)\n- A compass shows your heading direction\n- Statistics (pixels, distance, speed) update in real time\n- Low-power mode is available for longer walking sessions";
"help.manual.manual_drawing_title" = "Manual Drawing";
"help.manual.manual_drawing_desc" = "Place pixels directly on the map by tapping.\n\nDrawing Modes:\n- Color: Choose from preset colors or pick a custom color, then tap the map\n- Emoji: Select an emoji and tap to place it\n- Pattern: Use alliance flags or custom patterns\n\nSwitch modes using the drawing mode panel at the bottom of the map screen.";
"help.manual.map_explore_title" = "Map & Explore";
"help.manual.map_explore_desc" = "The map is your canvas.\n\n- Pinch to zoom, drag to pan across the world\n- Tap any pixel to see who drew it and when\n- Alliance flags appear on the map where teams dominate\n- Use the Explore panel to discover nearby hotspots\n- Event zones are highlighted during active competitions\n\nMap Features:\n- Nearby Players: See who's drawing nearby in real time\n- Region Info Bar: Shows area name, active players, pixel count, and controlling alliance\n- Territory Control: Alliance territories are displayed as colored zones on the map\n- Quick Stats: Floating widget showing today's pixels, sessions, and daily task progress";
"help.manual.history_title" = "Feed Center";
"help.manual.history_desc" = "The Feed tab is your content hub with three sections:\n\n- Feed: See drawing activities, achievement unlocks, and rank changes from players you follow. Like and comment on posts. Tap \"Fly to\" to visit a drawing location on the map.\n- Records: View all your past drawings in gallery or list format. Tap any session for full details, stats, and map replay. Share to social media or save as image.\n- Stats: Your personal data dashboard with activity calendar (heatmap), weekly trends, and city footprint — track your drawing journey over time.";
"help.manual.shop_title" = "Shop & Items";
"help.manual.shop_desc" = "Buy items with points in the Shop.\n\nItem Types:\n- Bombs: Clear other players' pixels in a target area\n- Boost Cards: Increase GPS drawing efficiency\n- Ads: Place your custom image on the map (requires review)\n- Custom Flags: Upload a custom flag for your alliance\n\nPoints & Wallet:\n- Earn points through check-ins, achievements, events, and invites\n- Recharge points via WeChat Pay or Alipay\n- View purchased items in your Backpack (Me > My Items)";
"help.manual.alliance_title" = "Alliance & Territory";
"help.manual.alliance_desc" = "Team up with other players to conquer territory.\n\nCreate an Alliance:\n- Go to the Alliance tab and tap Create\n- Set a name, description, visibility, and flag pattern\n\nAlliance Flags:\n- Color: Simple solid color\n- Emoji: Flag with an emoji icon\n- Complex: Upload a custom pattern image\n\nAlliance Growth:\n- Alliance Level: Earn XP through member activities to level up your alliance and unlock perks\n- Alliance Check-in: Members check in daily to earn points for the alliance\n- Contribution Ranking: See which members contribute the most pixels\n\nManagement:\n- Leader can promote admins, kick members, or transfer leadership\n- Invite new members with invite codes\n- View alliance stats: total pixels, territory, world ranking\n\nTerritory:\n- Alliances that dominate an area control its territory\n- Territory zones are shown as colored overlays on the map\n- Tap a territory to see the alliance breakdown";
"help.manual.achievements_title" = "Achievements";
"help.manual.achievements_desc" = "Unlock achievements by completing activities.\n\nCategories: Drawing, Social, Alliance, Shop, Activity, Special\n\nRarity Levels: Common, Uncommon, Rare, Epic, Legendary\n\nHow it works:\n- Achievements unlock automatically as you play\n- Claim point rewards on the Achievements page (Me > Achievements)\n- Share achievement cards to social media\n- Earned badges appear on your profile's honor wall";
"help.manual.events_title" = "Events & Challenges";
"help.manual.events_desc" = "Compete in time-limited events for special rewards.\n\nEvent Types:\n- Leaderboard Sprint: Draw the most pixels to rank high\n- Territory War: Fight to control map areas\n- Cooperation: All players work toward a shared goal\n- Faction War: Alliance vs. alliance battles\n\nHow to participate:\n- Check the Event Center (Me > Event Center)\n- Sign up individually or as an alliance\n- Enter event zones on the map to contribute\n- Rewards are distributed when events end";
"help.manual.drift_bottle_title" = "Drift Bottles";
"help.manual.drift_bottle_desc" = "Leave messages for strangers in bottles that travel the world.\n\nEarning Bottles:\n- Draw pixels to earn drift bottles (progress shown on screen)\n\nCreating:\n- After a drawing session, write a short message (up to 50 chars) and throw the bottle\n\nFinding:\n- Encounter bottles while drawing\n- Open to read messages, leave your own, or release it to continue drifting\n\nJourney Cards:\n- After 5 people open a bottle, it sinks and all participants receive a journey card\n- Collect cards in Me > Journey Collection";
"help.manual.leaderboard_title" = "Leaderboard";
"help.manual.leaderboard_desc" = "See how you rank against other players.\n\nTime Periods: Daily, Weekly, Monthly, All-Time\n\nRanking Types:\n- Personal: Individual pixel count\n- Alliance: Total alliance pixels and territory\n- City: Most active cities worldwide\n- Friends: Rankings among players you follow\n\nFeatures:\n- Rank Tiers: Earn rank badges (Bronze to Legend) based on your pixel count\n- Personal Rank Card: Your rank, tier badge, and stats displayed at the top\n- Top 3 Podium: The top 3 players are showcased with a special podium\n- Rank Changes: Animated indicators show how your rank has moved";
"help.manual.daily_tasks_title" = "Daily Tasks";
"help.manual.daily_tasks_desc" = "Complete daily tasks to earn bonus rewards.\n\nHow it works:\n- Each day, a set of tasks is generated for you (e.g., draw pixels, check in, explore the map)\n- Track your progress on each task with progress bars\n- Claim rewards for each completed task\n- Complete ALL tasks to unlock a special bonus reward\n\nAccess daily tasks from:\n- Me > Daily Tasks\n- The Quick Stats widget on the map (tap \"View Tasks\")\n\nTask progress updates automatically as you play. Don't forget — tasks reset daily!";
"help.manual.social_title" = "Social & Follow";
"help.manual.social_desc" = "Connect with other players and build your community.\n\nFollow System:\n- Follow players from their profile, leaderboard, or nearby player cards\n- View your followers and following lists from your profile\n- See activity from players you follow in the Feed tab\n\nNearby Players:\n- Active players drawing near you appear on the map\n- Tap a player chip to see their info and follow them\n- The region info bar shows how many players are active in your area\n\nSocial Feed:\n- Like and comment on drawings and achievements\n- Tap \"Fly to\" on a drawing post to visit the location on the map";
"help.manual.invite_title" = "Invite Friends";
"help.manual.invite_desc" = "Invite friends and earn bonus points.\n\nHow to invite:\n- Go to Me > Invite Friends\n- Copy or share your unique invite code\n- Your friend enters the code after signing up\n\nRewards:\n- You earn points for each successful invite\n- Your friend receives welcome bonus points\n- Track your invite stats on the invite page";
"help.manual.settings_title" = "Settings & Profile";
"help.manual.settings_desc" = "Customize your experience.\n\n- Edit Profile: Change nickname, motto, and avatar\n- Display: Adjust font size (Compact, Medium, Large)\n- Language: Switch app language or follow system setting\n- Sound: Toggle sound effects\n- Privacy: Hide your nickname, alliance info, or flag from others\n- Daily Check-in: Sign in daily for streak rewards, weekly reward cycles, and milestone bonuses (30/90/180/365 days)\n- Daily Tasks: Complete daily tasks like drawing pixels, checking in, and exploring the map to earn bonus rewards\n- Follow & Fans: View your followers and the players you follow from your profile";
"help.feedback.section" = "Your Feedback";
"help.feedback.placeholder" = "Tell us your suggestions or issues...";
